                                <settlement ref="http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/687928">Jerusalem</settlement>
                                <geogName type="site">'En Ya'al burial cave</geogName>
                                <geogFeat type="locus"/>
                            </placeName>
                            <p>Found in the standing pit of the rock-hewn burial cave (L10, B123),
                                which was filled with human skeletons, oil lamps, potsherds and
                                glass vessels.</p>
                        </origin>
